      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/5bb32230813ab6c05g019d49?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=41476&rangeEnd=41493"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300014139_9_5192-5228",
      "chapterUid": 9,
      "range": "5192-5228",
      "markText": "有时会以情绪危机为突出的特点，而这种危机正是为进一步的人格发展奠定基础。",
      "totalCount": 36,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300014139&chapterUid=9&rangeStart=5192&rangeEnd=5228",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/5bb32230813ab6c05g019d49?chapterUid=9&rangeStart=5192&rangeEnd=5228"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300014139_9_5329-5372",
      "chapterUid": 9,
      "range": "5329-5372",
      "markText": "埃里克森认为，如果年轻人不能对他人做出深刻的个人承诺，他们就可能会变得过分孤僻或自恋。",
      "totalCount": 36,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300014139&chapterUid=9&rangeStart=5329&rangeEnd=5372",
